UI for Neti Neti Taxon Finder and Reconciliation tools

DIRS and FILES:
1) ./sinatra/tmp - chmod 777
2) in localhost dir (or any reached via URL) simlink from 
  a) ./webservices/texts/master_lists
  b) ./sinatra/tmp
3) tf py server should be in the same dir as NetiNeti files (or they should be in a PATH)
copy L-server-test.py, recons_server.py into py_server with all NetiNeti files (from on BoA svn)

RUN:
Neti Neti TF (server/client - port 1234, service 4567):
Reconciliation (server/client - port 3002, service 3000):
UI (port 3001) - names_tools.rb

tools_dir=your_dir_with_servers_web-services_sinatra_app

cd $tools_dir/py_server/
python L-server-test.py &
python recons_server.py &
cd $tools_dir/webservices/
ruby taxon_finder_web_service.rb &
ruby reconcile_web_service.rb -p 3000 &
cd $tools_dir/sinatra/
ruby names_tools.rb -p 3001 &


STOP:
after killing all 5 processes do:
rm $tools_dir/sinatra/tmp/*

